HEADWORD: Tube-shell
<hw>Tube"-shell`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any bivalve mollusk which secretes a shelly tube around its siphon,
as the watering-shell.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

